<FIRST>u i PM-Czechoslovakia     01-10 0310</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Czechoslovakia,0321</SECOND>
<HEAD>Police Question Havel, Charter 77 Spokeswoman</HEAD>
<DATELINE>VIENNA, Austria (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Police in Czechoslovakia questioned banned
playwright and human rights activist Vaclav Havel about an anonymous
threat of self-immolation at an anti-government rally planned for
Sunday, he said today.
   Czechoslovak authorities banned the weekend rally and the
Communist Party's chief ideologist warned Monday of threats to
